						               													<description>Los Futbol&amp;iacute;simos is a simple and fast card game in which you are going to send your best players to steal balls and score many goals. But before, you are going to have to assemble the goal!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Los Futbol&amp;iacute;simos is a collection of adventures, friendship, mystery and football. This game starts with a strange invitation. Los Futbol&amp;iacute;simos are summoned to the Campo4 tournament. It is a very mysterious tournament with rules on the field of play that are very different from those known. Nothing there is what it seems. The adventure of playing with Los Futbol&amp;iacute;simos in Campo 4 and overcoming the challenge to win the match is shared.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each of the characters will have an associated action. The objective will be to have the greatest number of balls of the same color as the associated goal.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There will be a total of four goals, being necessary for each player to have their own to end the game. The colored balls multiply throughout the competition, going from goal to goal. The goals will not be decided until the end.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On each turn, you have to decide which is the best action to apply. It is also essential to know when to use certain key cards such as the free kick, the referee, the VAR... And of course you have to be flexible because the game is constantly changing.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
